---

<Layout
  title="Commercial Flooring Phoenix | Office, Retail & Industrial Flooring - Brooks Floor Covering"
  description="Commercial flooring services in Phoenix. Carpet tile, LVP, epoxy, polished concrete for offices, retail, restaurants, and industrial spaces. Free estimates ‚Äî call (623) 688-8422."
