            Our Clients
          </p>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-brand-dark font-display tracking-tight">
            Trusted by Leading Organizations
          </h2>
        </div>

        <div
          class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8 items-center justify-items-center max-w-6xl mx-auto"
        >
          {
            trustedOrgs.map((org) => (
              <div class="flex items-center justify-center p-4">
                <img
                  src={org.logo}
                  alt={`${org.name} logo`}
                  class="w-32 h-auto max-h-16 object-contain grayscale hover:grayscale-0 hover:scale-110 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300"
                  width="128"
                  height="64"
                  loading="lazy"
                />
              </div>
            ))
          }
        </div>
        <p class="text-center text-neutral-500 text-sm mt-10 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          We have had the privilege of providing flooring services to the organizations listed
          above, both through direct partnerships and through our work as a trusted subcontractor
          alongside general contractors. This list reflects completed projects and professional
          relationships ‚Äî not endorsements.
        </p>
