              <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                Our installers are certified by Mohawk, Shaw, Arizona Tile, and Daltile for
                commercial-grade product handling.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div
                class="w-14 h-14 bg-blue-50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-2xl mx-auto mb-4"
                aria-hidden="true"
